org.cip4.elk.alces.test
Interface TestSession

All Known Implementing Classes:
TestSessionImpl, TestSessionNode
public interface TestSession

A class that represents a test session. A test session consists of a set of related messages that are sent and received and on which tests are run.

Author:
Claes Buckwalter (clabu@itn.liu.se)
